# Route security

- Every route under app/api/** must verify Firebase Admin token server-side before body parsing.
- Credit deduction must be atomic (Firestore transaction), never read-then-write.
- `analyze/route.ts` and `pdf/route.ts` currently lack both — flag any edit to these files that doesn't add auth+credit check.
